{"tid":93532,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"月供基金討論","createTime":"2017-01-24T13:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T17:08:21.000Z","uid":23968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abd89d297e5a4d1a5065f5c68c27e8895c321857","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"好似無見過人開post 講基金<br />\n有無人有投資開基金？<br />\n<br />\n我本身間唔時都Keep 住學投資學左幾年<br />\n有玩過正股 期指 牛熊 <br />\n但最尾發覺香港個市太難玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢排月供緊基金 發覺成效唔錯 <br />\n有無人一齊交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己就去fsm呢個平台到自己慢慢揀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 追數基金佬死開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非打手 純討論"},{"pid":"252aaa4582c69a31c89920bb5bcce2033b8553dd","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"連登無人玩基金？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0768d16f9b5c53948e7c7c081c9b53e9e0f929c8","tid":93532,"uid":182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:12:11.000Z","msg":"唔想比錢基金佬賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a9494794eca6b3920ca426fd9282c95f52fdb4","tid":93532,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"其實可以點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：完全唔識投資野"},{"pid":"598a1c365cf3db734db8f3563c75d91a5069429f","tid":93532,"uid":79141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：完全唔識投資野</blockquote><br />\n同問！ 學野"},{"pid":"201d132ae481cf00496d3705cde33d279d97b714","tid":93532,"uid":29608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"研究緊債券， 想leverage 買債"},{"pid":"6cb8d7bfc4d03db66b844cc717420a3fb1129d89","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：完全唔識投資野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最簡單就月供唔洗煩 好處可以睇返成本平均法<br />\n我都搵緊有無其他基金平台 <br />\n一般黎講銀行同分銷商<br />\n銀行我唔熟 分銷商我就係<a href=\"http://www.fundsupermart.com.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fundsupermart.com.hk%2F&d=VfU7UGqeyHdBUD1vc26TcXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5f443770\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fundsupermart.com.hk/</a> 睇 佢都好大 有好多 基金可以慢慢睇慢慢揀 <br />\n揀完你再去morningstar 睇評論咁"},{"pid":"02aa295a722f3d093a8299c141dac403e073267b","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>研究緊債券， 想leverage 買債</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有睇過 但就咁買債成本極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fe52a2d47acb086f136c9b29ef9f8264b2cde2","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想比錢基金佬賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己無時間管理無計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235e0861e284473fff4abb0925ab9c660e99e016","tid":93532,"uid":62059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"月供基金不如月供2800<br />\n夠錢開美股Account既可以每月買VT + BND + BNDX"},{"pid":"fcefb71fb97d4c2e345353316eb2f8d1fe890a36","tid":93532,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月供基金不如月供2800<br />\n夠錢開美股Account既可以每月買<span style=\"color: red;\">VT + BND + BNDX</span></blockquote><br />\n美股收息要扣30%血...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd61fb240cb66d461409467863a45ec45992946","tid":93532,"uid":36390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T18:39:44.000Z","msg":"收費係點，買開邊類型基金"},{"pid":"d0a48abdd9cdcb470f9b0a33921e91fdae8b059a","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>月供基金不如月供2800<br />\n夠錢開美股Account既可以每月買VT + BND + BNDX</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前高登有post 開月供2800 <br />\n每個月貼晒圖出黎<br />\n（依家連登呢邊個post無貼圖？）<br />\n<br />\n但睇返佢回報率都唔高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就咁睇上年 恆指回報率得1%多d<br />\n再講就係唔想限於香港市場太單一<br />\n基金可以用小本都做到風險分散"},{"pid":"d243617e2eee4bfe03407d29ecbf0a7c846e43ab","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>月供基金不如月供2800<br />\n夠錢開美股Account既可以每月買<span style=\"color: red;\">VT + BND + BNDX</span></blockquote><br />\n美股收息要扣30%血...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVt bnd bndx 唔識求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071b1db499cc82dbbd4a7fbd27e93c52764d0861","tid":93532,"uid":23968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收費係點，買開邊類型基金</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同平台有唔同 通常買就認購費<br />\n有d基金會收年管理費 （多數反映價格上）<br />\n同賣收贖回費（個別基金先有）"},{"pid":"0d5ac14f4d26132bd166b6097b549bb02a766fbe","tid":93532,"uid":62059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>月供基金不如月供2800<br />\n夠錢開美股Account既可以每月買<span style=\"color: red;\">VT + BND + BNDX</span></blockquote><br />\n美股收息要扣30%血...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nVt bnd bndx 唔識求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" c